{
  "chapter": 90,
  "chapter_summary": "第九十回 鸿门宴。伴花君简召舞为女儿满月大摆筵席于鹦鹉洲铁网帮总堂，太阳门掌门秦百龄率一百二十名弟子前来贺喜，实则挑衅。丑尼姑携四位无影门蒙面女子闯入。秦百龄提出两门弟子比武一百二十场，以死亡人数定胜负。无影门女子专杀月形门得胜弟子，残臂叟（实为芮玮化装）受财宝之诱出手相助，专杀太阳门得胜者。秦百龄暗中求旧识秋萍（丑尼姑）相助，残臂叟以将来索代价为条件退出。双方各凭真实力量较量，简召舞暗中在酒中下毒，迷倒众人后命弟子擒拿。残臂叟露出真功夫突围，丑尼姑与四位蒙面女子（包括白燕）合力杀出。白燕呼芮玮之名暴露其身份，简召舞惊恐芮玮死而复活。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日，小女弥月之喜，亦是本门复门周年纪念，敬请各位赏脸的朋友尽量开怀畅饮，招待不周，多多包涵。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秦老英雄也来啦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦老英雄驾到，本帮何等荣幸，速摆上桌！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "一桌不够，请摆十桌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "老英雄随来多少弟子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "本门前来贺喜弟子，不多不少，一共一百二十名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦掌门今日何兴，率来这么多弟子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "怎样？贵帮怕被本门弟子吃倒吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "请问秦掌门，贵门如何称呼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "本门小门小派，名称何堪一道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "此人到底什么来头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "属下只知秦百龄在江湖上名头甚著，武功颇有几下。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "你难道不知他是那一门的掌门？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "年来仅知秦百龄在云贵一带成立一派，派名却不听传说，好像秦老儿有意不向天下宣布门派之名。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "你去小心通知本帮所有帮众，严密戒备，再来贺客一律不令踏上鹦鹉洲。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "这样一来不是坏了帮主之兴？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "事急从权，哼，他们敢有什么异变的话，教他们来得去不得！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不准进去，不准进去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "迎宾客",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "来人不愿通报姓名，打伤本帮弟子硬闯而进！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "大师为何不肯道出姓名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "贵帮既开盛筵，广迎宾客，又何必要来客道出姓名？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "本帮虽然广迎宾客却怕宵小之徒闯进，大师倘若自认非宵小之徒，何不留下姓名，将来也好登门谢礼！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "谢礼不敢，请问贵帮到底肯不肯招待咱们叨扰一顿？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "大师不道姓名来历，恕不招待！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "咱们此来并非白白叨扰，酒完后贫尼为你们大做法场时，一切免费！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "本帮要做什么法场，大师若不退回，莫怪在下无礼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "好啊，贫尼此来亦算贺客之一，倒要看你如何无礼斥退咱们？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "南天，赐坐，免得扰了小女弥月的喜意！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对，对，这样才像话，还是贵帮帮主气魄够，哪像你们狗腿子，招待还要来客道出姓名来历，简直小气得紧。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位尽请欢饮，本帮备有数百坛花雕，不愁饮之不够！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "伴花君，今日之筵可否来点余兴节目？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "莫非秦掌门有什高见？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "不错，本人确有一点建议，我一百二十名弟子不能白白吃喝，这余兴节目就由他们凑合可好？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "你若有意助兴，尽请提示，本君必不教你失望。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "好，咱们先干一杯！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "余兴节目还请你掌门派下一百二十名弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "节目如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "就由月形门弟子与本弟子较艺一百二十场，以之助兴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦掌门此来有意较艺的啰？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "非也，非也，这不过本人预先为阁下安排的余兴节目。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，不错，秦老头的主意不错，比啊，比啊！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好主意，好主意……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "命齐治平老师选来一百二十名弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是喜宴，为求助兴，双方点到即收。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死啦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么杀起人啦？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "齐治平",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "一群妖女，好狠的手段，出来，出来，齐某人来会你四位，有本领向齐某人招呼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "大师，那四位年轻女子可是你的弟子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "不是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "她四人与你什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "目前没有关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "怎说目前没有关系！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "目前她四位负责杀人，我却不杀人，倒是事后替所有死者做个法场，相谢叨扰之意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "你们还未吃喝一点，何谓叨扰？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "既据此桌总算叨扰，她们四位办事的原则，事情不办完不吃不喝！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "你们可是受人之托？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "不错，受人之托，忠人所事，我劝你不必打算问得太多，免得告诉你，令你难堪！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "本帮帮主意思，余兴节目不用比了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "也好，就请贵帮帮主当众宣告，月形门一百二十名弟子不是太阳门一百二十名弟子的对手。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "太阳门？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦掌门，你可知今日是我小女弥月之庆？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "这正是最好的机会，当此天下各门各派齐集的时候，你我两家斗过真章，不是你死便是我亡。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦掌门就不能今日事后，再谈本门与太阳门之争？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "不能！除非月形门今日声称不是世仇太阳门之敌，否则小老儿决不退去！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦百龄，今日是我帮之喜，你不要嚣张太盛！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "眼看灭亡在即，还顾忌什么喜事！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦掌门，我今日声称本门不是太阳门之敌后，是否就此退去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "当然，你自知不敌，咱们也就不为已甚，只是第二日起，月形门从此解散！还有，贵帮跟着也要解散！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦百龄，你欺人太甚！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "你要不服气，我一百二十名弟子在此，随你哪个去斗，只要你不死，我佩服你，叫你爷爷。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "阁下神气个什么，你以为买通那四位女子便能歼灭我帮吗？去将帮主库中聚宝箱抬来。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "此箱财宝价值连城，为天池府三代珍藏，现在全送给大师。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "你有何求？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "秦百龄求大师的一切，希大师反其道行之。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "第一场双方六胜六负，不分上下，现在再比第二。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "好啊，咱们就以一百二十名弟子为赌，他们斗完后，哪一方弟子死亡的多，便从此解散本门如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "就这么说！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "你是什么人，敢做得主？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "帮主之意如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "就这么说定！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "大师，你，你，这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "这箱珠宝搬过去！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "你嫌它不够？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "不是不够，而是你求错了对像！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "前辈有何教我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "无影门替雇主办事一向负责到底，决不背叛雇主，你就是再加十倍的财宝，那四位年轻女子亦不会帮你杀死太阳门得胜的弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "残废老头，你倒知之本门甚多！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "你既不可能求动她们反其道行之，不如求我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "前辈能够相助吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "你将那箱财宝抬到我桌上，我保月形门不输太阳门。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好吧，开始比第三场。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "残废老头，你敢坏无影门生意，小心脑袋搬家！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "丑老尼，残老头可没坏你无影门生意吧，你们杀你们的，我杀我的，互不相干。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "残废老头，不要太得意了，小心笑坏了肚子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦百龄，再比第四场！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "残臂老头，我太阳门与你何冤何仇？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "这不是冤仇的问题，而是金钱问题，阁下能够付我多出这箱天池府三代珍藏的财宝，我残臂叟立即反背助你，我不像无影门，不专做这种生意，不必做出信用，以便以后财源不绝，我只要捞一大票就行啦！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "四场比赛，贵方十六胜，我方三十二胜，你月形门还好意思与本门争吗？趁早宣布解散，免得十场下来，输得太多，于你铁网帮主的名头有损。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦掌门，你先前说过的话，不要忘记得太快，记得你说哪一方弟子死亡得多，便算输，可没说哪一方胜的多算赢呀！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "谁不清楚，你才一一面授十二名弟子故意装败，说来为此装败，够丢人的了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "求胜为上，再者保命要紧，你不妨也学学我教贵弟子装着不胜，也可保命不死，只是如此来看，余下六场比完，双方皆和，算起来仍是你败。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "我方胜了三十二场，怎说我败？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "但你死了二十名弟子，却比本门十六位数多出四位，秦掌门，你是败定了，赶明早起遵守诺言解散太阳门吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "六场未比，还不知谁方弟子死的多呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "你要有兴趣比，继续比吧，只要你嫌贵门弟子命太长的话，不妨叫他们多胜几场。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "秋萍，你一定要助我！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "我只能尽我个人力量助你，要知我无能指挥她们四位。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "秋萍，只要你出手，那残废老儿不是你对手。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "我功夫荒废了很久，只怕不是那老儿的对手呢！",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "残老头，我有句话不知你愿不愿听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "小老儿洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "你可愿卖个交情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "你说出来看看，我看值不值得卖再决定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "你我双方不要再管此间之事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "假若我不答应呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "那就在六场未比之前，你我先分一个胜负。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "这个嘛，小老儿不愿结下强敌。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "你不愿结仇敌无影门，就请卖个交情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "小老儿惟利是图，请问卖下这交情代价如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "我无影门自会记着相报的一天。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "这么回答不够实际。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "前辈，你不能收了财宝，中途变志。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "中途变志？太难听，太难听了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "前辈不要忘记，曾保证咱们不输对方！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "不错，我是这么说过，那是看有一箱珠宝的分上，现在珠宝还你，请抬回吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "前辈，你，你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "text": "珠宝还你我说出的话也收回！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "丑老尼，听到没有，小老儿损失了一箱珠宝呀！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "你说要什么代价。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "我现在一时想不起来有何代价相索，只要你此时切实地答应将来我索代价时，不得推辞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "好吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "当此天下英雄面前，一言为定。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "秋萍，多谢你啦。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "伴花君，现在开始比下去，你我都不要倚靠他人，各凭真实力量比下去。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "本应如此，只怪阁下先存不良意图。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒中有毒！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皆入吾彀中矣！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不准留一个活口逃出！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "咱们联手突围！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ping",
      "speaker_name": "秋萍",
      "listener": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "text": "你到底是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_bi_sou",
      "speaker_name": "残臂叟",
      "listener": "char_qiu_ping",
      "text": "小老儿残臂叟也！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮，你还不快来助我！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "白燕，不要怕，我来了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
